<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200813/17954fb9e8364b428aa94ce45375df4e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200813/d20e7c1b90634e218ce2fcedc728fa0a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>▼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200813/eeae879caf28469a8679fc9795155047.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如你所见</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">几乎没有年轻人能活着走出这片战场</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">特别是在夏天，进一趟厨房</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就会湿一次身，堪比人间修罗场</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而上班累了一天</p>
